    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S54 platform. This unit features a 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double VANOS system, delivering linear power through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is structurally pristine, having undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure torsional rigidity. The limited-slip differential operates with factory-spec lockup, and the suspension retains its original kinematics with no bushing deflection. Finished in a mirror-like Carbon Black, the exterior is free of rock chips or oxidative wear, while the undercarriage presents in a dry, corrosion-free state. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
