      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that redefines the standard for showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, glass-like luster with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery retains its factory matte finish and original scent, with absolutely no bolster wear or carpet staining. All electronics, switches, and high-resolution displays function with crisp, tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists using genuine OEM parts. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Complete service documentation, original window sticker, and all keys are included.",
